{"data": {"repository": {"pullRequest": {"id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0MzYyMjE5NzI0", "number": 624, "title": "getBytes uses the platform charset by default.", "bodyText": "As far as I can see, the only place where the schemas are loaded into the cache is loadSchemasIntoCache, where they are extracted from an XML Document. As such, they won't have an associated encoding. The XMLSource defaults to UTF-8, so this blows up if you have special characters and, for example, windows-1252 as the platform charset.", "createdAt": "2020-01-13T16:53:04Z", "url": "https://github.com/apache/cxf/pull/624", "merged": true, "mergeCommit": {"oid": "543521ab051cb4f199faeab5765d001920bbbba2"}, "closed": true, "closedAt": "2020-01-14T12:35:06Z", "author": {"login": "NaridaL"}, "timelineItems": {"totalCount": 6, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABb5_SiogH2gAyMzYyMjE5NzI0OjExMWZlNTA3ODFhM2M2NjU0YTQxNDM1ZTA4YzdkOTZjMDU1ZmNjZjg=", "endCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABb6QMwWgFqTM0MjQ5ODc3OA==", "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": [{"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "111fe50781a3c6654a41435e08c7d96c055fccf8", "author": {"user": {"login": "NaridaL", "name": "Adrian Leonhard"}}, "url": "https://github.com/apache/cxf/commit/111fe50781a3c6654a41435e08c7d96c055fccf8", "committedDate": "2020-01-13T16:52:53Z", "message": "getBytes uses the platform charset by default.\n\nAs far as I can see, the only place where the schemas are loaded into the cache is loadSchemasIntoCache, where they are extracted from an XML Document. As such, they won't have an associated encoding. The XMLSource defaults to UTF-8, so this blows up if you have special characters and, for example, windows-1252 as the platform charset."}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "b8dea308649c0141051fca766f7db2fb27d5a738", "author": {"user": {"login": "NaridaL", "name": "Adrian Leonhard"}}, "url": "https://github.com/apache/cxf/commit/b8dea308649c0141051fca766f7db2fb27d5a